00:44:30.790 --> 00:44:33.426
I think the ideas, actually,
are super easy and not

00:44:33.426 --> 00:44:34.300
hard to come up with.

00:44:34.300 --> 00:44:37.370
The hard part's, who's
going to do it for 20 years?

00:44:37.370 --> 00:44:40.840
And so what we've found is
it's easier to find the idea

00:44:40.840 --> 00:44:42.340
than it is to find the person.

00:44:42.340 --> 00:44:45.637
So Miss Kim is our
newest business,

00:44:45.637 --> 00:44:47.470
which is our Korean
restaurant in Kerrytown.

00:44:47.470 --> 00:44:52.510
So that's probably five or six
years of work by Ji Hye with us

00:44:52.510 --> 00:44:54.760
