a lot of interactivity

00:45:05.410 --> 00:45:07.570
because when you're
working collaboratively,

00:45:07.570 --> 00:45:10.060
you need to be able to
incorporate other people's

00:45:10.060 --> 00:45:14.760
ideas, yet stand true to your
own, et cetera, et cetera.

00:45:14.760 --> 00:45:16.540
And that's how they come.

00:45:16.540 --> 00:45:19.690
Internally, for smaller
things, the biggest thing is--

00:45:19.690 --> 00:45:21.940
there were a few of those
Bottom Line Change pamphlets

00:45:21.940 --> 00:45:22.440
over there.

00:45:22.440 --> 00:45:24.880
So we have a change methodology.

00:45:24.880 --> 00:45:26.709
And because a lot
of our approach

00:45:26.709 --> 00:45:28.750
is to teach everybody how
to lead from the minute

00:45:28.750 --> 00:45:31.120
they start working and
not wait until they

00:45:31.120 --> 00:45:34.940
get a title, which doesn't
really mean anything,

00:45:34.940 --> 00:45:38.440
that the idea is that when
somebody has an idea that they

00:45:38.440 --> 00:45:39.400
can lead the change.

00:45:39.400 --> 00:45:41.085
Now, they may not be
the decision-maker,

00:45:41.085 --> 00:45:43.210
but that doesn't stop them
from leading the change.

00:45:43.210 --> 00:45:46.600
And so my job becomes to coach
them in how to lead the change,

00:45:46.600 --> 00:45:49.180
not to implement their
idea for them, which

00:45:49.180 --> 00:45:52.060
is, I would suggest, very
parental and paternalistic

00:45:52.060 --> 00:45:53.275
and not very helpful.

00:45:53.275 --> 00:45:55.150
It's better than not
implementing their idea,

00:45:55.150 --> 00:45:57.730
but I think the real thing
is to learn how to lead.

00:45:57.730 --> 00:45:59.112
And the pushback
is, well, people

00:45:59.112 --> 00:46:00.320
aren't going to listen to me.

00:46:00.320 --> 00:46:02.530
I'm like, dude, they don't
listen to me, either.

00:46:02.530 --> 00:46:05.590
That's what leadership is, is
how do you get people on board?

00:46:05.590 --> 00:46:07.870
Because there's
always resistance.

00:46:07.870 --> 00:46:09.880
So that's the two,
for a business

00:46:09.880 --> 00:46:11.275
and for a smaller change.

