00:46:49.860 --> 00:46:52.540
Today, everybody could
do food photography

00:46:52.540 --> 00:46:53.649
and you all could have--

00:46:53.649 --> 00:46:55.690
in this room, at least--
you could have a website

00:46:55.690 --> 00:46:57.877
up by 3 o'clock.

00:46:57.877 --> 00:46:59.710
But in those days, we
didn't have any money.

00:46:59.710 --> 00:47:02.982
So food photography,
it used to cost $10,000

00:47:02.982 --> 00:47:05.440
